ECM Real Estate Creditors Vote for Bankruptcy, Hospodarske Says

-- B y   K r y s t o f   C h a m o n i k o l a s
-- 
2011-07-21T06:16:52Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-21/ecm-real-estate-creditors-vote-for-bankruptcy-hospodarske-says.html
ECM Real Estate Investments AG (ECM)  will
be declared bankrupt by a Prague court today or tomorrow after
creditors of the Czech developer yesterday rejected a debt
reorganization plan,  Hospodarske Noviny  newspaper reported,
without saying where it obtained the information.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Krystof Chamonikolas in Prague at 
 kchamonikola@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Gavin Serkin at   gserkin@bloomberg.net  